<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/feb/16/">&#x27a0;</a> February 16, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="audiosurf-ride-your-music" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.audio-surf.com/">Audiosurf: Ride Your Music</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>An outstandingly fun Windows game: Drive a car over coloured blocks on a track generated by an MP3 of your choosing.  Pick something mellow, and you get a relaxing low-scoring game.  But if you want a challenge, throw some pumping techno its way.  Works very well with Chemical Brothers and Pixies, I find.  Best use of Digital Signal Processing ever!</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
